description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces 2". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Asakusa, Tokyo
-Osaka Castle, Osaka
-Shureimon Gate of Shuri Castle, Okinawa
-Kobe Meriken Park, Hyogo
-Nara Park, Nara
-Yokohama Minato Mirai, Kanagawa
-Niseko, Hokkaido
-Lake Kawaguchi and Mt.Fuji, Yamanashi
-Higashiyama, Kyoto
-Ginzan Onsen, Yamagata
name: The Beauty of Japan's Landmarks
